---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Legal Disclaimer — LDR Visa"
  description="LDR Visa legal disclaimer — this site provides general immigration information only and does not constitute legal advice."
  noindex={true}
>
<style>
  .page-wrap {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  }
  .page-header {
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: .4rem;
  }
  .page-header p {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: .9rem;
  }
  .notice-box {
    background: #fef3c7;
    border: 1px solid #fde68a;
    border-left: 5px solid #f59e0b;
    border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .notice-box p {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #92400e;
    font-size: .95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin: 2rem 0 .6rem;
  }
  p {
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: .95rem;
  }
  ul {
    color: #374151;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: .95rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  li { margin-bottom: .35rem; }
  a { color: #2563eb; text-decoration: underline; }
</style>

<div class="page-wrap">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Legal Disclaimer</h1>
    <p>Last updated: April 30, 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="notice-box">
    <p>LDR Visa provides general immigration information for educational purposes only. Nothing on this Site constitutes legal advice, and no attorney-client relationship is formed by using this Site. Immigration law is complex and fact-specific — always consult a licensed immigration attorney for advice about your individual situation.</p>
  </div>

  <h2>1. Not Legal Advice</h2>
  <p>The content published on ldrvisa.org is intended for general informational purposes only. It does not constitute legal advice, legal opinion, or any form of legal representation. The information on this Site may not reflect the most current legal developments, and laws and regulations change frequently.</p>
  <p>LDR Visa is not a law firm. None of the authors, editors, or contributors to this Site are acting as your attorney. Accessing or using this Site does not create an attorney-client relationship between you and LDR Visa or any individual associated with this Site.</p>

  <h2>2. No Guarantee of Accuracy</h2>
  <p>While we make every effort to provide accurate, up-to-date information, immigration law is subject to frequent change by Congress, USCIS, the Department of State, and federal courts. We cannot guarantee that all information on this Site is current, complete, or accurate at the time you read it.</p>
  <p>Government processing times, fee amounts, form versions, and eligibility requirements change regularly. Always verify critical information directly with official government sources:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.uscis.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">USCIS — U.S. Citizenship and Immigration Services (uscis.gov)</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://travel.state.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">U.S. Department of State — travel.state.gov</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.dhs.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Department of Homeland Security — dhs.gov</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Individual Circumstances Vary</h2>
  <p>Immigration eligibility and outcomes depend heavily on individual facts and circumstances. General information about the K-1 fiancé visa, CR-1 spousal visa, Adjustment of Status, or any other immigration benefit may not apply to your specific situation. Factors such as prior immigration history, criminal records, prior visa denials, country of birth, and relationship history can significantly affect your case.</p>
  <p>Do not make immigration decisions based solely on information found on this Site. Consult a licensed immigration attorney who can evaluate your specific facts before filing any petition or application.</p>

  <h2>4. Affiliate and Third-Party Links</h2>
  <p>This Site may contain links to third-party immigration service providers, legal services, financial services, and other resources. These links may be affiliate links, meaning we may receive compensation if you click a link and make a purchase or sign up for a service.</p>
  <p>The inclusion of any link does not imply our endorsement of the linked website or service. We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or practices of any third-party websites. References to specific service providers are not legal referrals and do not constitute a recommendation that you use any particular service.</p>
  <p>Non-attorney immigration services (such as document preparation services) are not a substitute for legal advice from a licensed immigration attorney.</p>

  <h2>5. No Guarantee of Outcome</h2>
  <p>Immigration applications involve discretionary decisions by government officers. We make no representations or guarantees regarding the outcome of any visa application, petition, or immigration process. Even a correctly filed, complete application may be denied based on officer discretion, policy changes, or factors specific to your case.</p>

  <h2>6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, LDR Visa and its authors, editors, and contributors shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of or reliance on the information provided on this Site. This includes, without limitation, damages for lost visa petitions, visa denials, attorney fees, or other immigration-related costs.</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to This Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>We reserve the right to update or modify this Disclaimer at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the Site. Your continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Disclaimer.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this Disclaimer, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:hello@ldrvisa.org">hello@ldrvisa.org</a></p>
</div>
</Base>
